OL,6,FGilbert Clarke, Age 97, RAF
OL,8,FInterviewed 4 July 2023
OL,10,FAfter lying about his age and
OL,11,Fvolunteering to join the RAF in his
OL,12,Fnative Jamaica, Gilbert Clarke was
OL,13,Fsent to Britain on a troop ship via
OL,14,Fthe United States.
