OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Gilbert
OL,4,CClarke
OL,6,FWhile training to service radar
OL,7,Fequipment he and his class saw the
OL,8,Fhundreds of aircraft passing overhead
OL,9,Fon 6 June en route to Normandy and
OL,10,Fcheered as they realised that the long-
OL,11,Fawaited invasion of occupied Europe
OL,12,Fhad begun.
OL,14,FHe said: "I used to repair the
OL,15,Fequipment, test and take them to
OL,16,Fplanes.
OL,18,F"At that time Britain was low on
OL,19,Fequipment so if things came in damaged
OL,20,Fwe tried to salvage what we could and
OL,21,Fput them back in the planes.
