OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Gilbert
OL,4,CClarke
OL,6,F"We were in the workshop mending bits
OL,7,Fand pieces, testing instruments, and
OL,8,Fwe could hear a droning noise.
OL,10,F"Think of it as one plane, think about
OL,11,Ffifty planes, think about five hundred
OL,12,Fplanes, think about a thousand planes.
OL,14,F"You couldn't see the sky, it was all
OL,15,Fblack with planes.
OL,17,F"We asked the Sergeant and he said
OL,18,F'This is it, they're going to Europe.'
OL,19,FAnd we all shouted 'Give them hell
OL,20,Fboys.'
