OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Gilbert
OL,4,CClarke
OL,6,F"It could have gone either way.
OL,8,F"Rough, anxious, scary.
OL,10,F"We hoped Britain and the world would
OL,11,Fbe a better place.
OL,13,F"Thanks to our cousins the Yanks for
OL,14,Fbringing in supplies so we could
OL,15,Fbreathe again."
